p: The Cytoscape plug-in ClueGO ( 12) and ReactomeFIViz ( 13) were applied for the differentially expressed proteins to process the Biological Process GO terms, and Kyoto Encyclopedia of Genes and Genomes (KEGG) pathway analysis ( www.genome.jp/kegg/). P<0.05 and FDR <0.01 were selected as threshold values for GO and KEGG pathway enrichment.
